    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited to share this absolute gem with you. This car is in such incredible shape\u2014it really looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one, and you won\u2019t find a single scratch or blemish anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm sad to see it go, but I know whoever gets it is going to absolutely love it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
