    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained to a standard that rivals its first day on the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the original scent of luxury remains intact. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive paper trail included. Always garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. It\u2019s not just a pre-owned vehicle; it\u2019s a preserved piece of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
