      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW's M-Division engineering, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been fully serviced. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Crucially, the chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the tactile feedback and neutral balance the E46 chassis is celebrated for. With zero deferred maintenance and all vitals within factory tolerances, this specimen offers a pure, analog driving experience in an aesthetically and mechanically pristine package.",
